{
  "video_id": "6PdetS6wzEM",
  "title": "Financial Statements - Lecture 1 - Uses and Users",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 10530.0,
      "end_time": 11210.0,
      "text": "Hi."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 11210.0,
      "end_time": 12510.0,
      "text": "Else Grech here."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 12510.0,
      "end_time": 16520.0,
      "text": "Today, we&#39;re going to be talking about financial statements."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 16520.0,
      "end_time": 18840.0,
      "text": "What is accounting?"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 18840.0,
      "end_time": 20720.0,
      "text": "Accounting is an information system"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 20720.0,
      "end_time": 24260.0,
      "text": "that identifies and records an organization&#39;s transactions"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 24260.0,
      "end_time": 26450.0,
      "text": "and then communicates them to a wide variety"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 26450.0,
      "end_time": 28550.0,
      "text": "of interested users."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 28550.0,
      "end_time": 30650.0,
      "text": "A knowledge of accounting is relevant and useful"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 30650.0,
      "end_time": 33220.0,
      "text": "in whatever career you decide to pursue,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 33220.0,
      "end_time": 37520.0,
      "text": "be it marketing or financial analyst."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 37520.0,
      "end_time": 40310.0,
      "text": "Every position requires some knowledge of accounting"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 40310.0,
      "end_time": 43460.0,
      "text": "or an understanding of how your actions in your position"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 43460.0,
      "end_time": 45320.0,
      "text": "will affect the business overall,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 45320.0,
      "end_time": 47480.0,
      "text": "both their profitability and their progress"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 47480.0,
      "end_time": 49660.0,
      "text": "as they move forward."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 49660.0,
      "end_time": 52790.0,
      "text": "You must be able to analyze the information from the past,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 52790.0,
      "end_time": 54730.0,
      "text": "so you can adjust what you do in the future"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 54730.0,
      "end_time": 59140.0,
      "text": "to ensure the company you own or work for is profitable."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 59140.0,
      "end_time": 61840.0,
      "text": "You need accounting information to make informed decisions"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 61840.0,
      "end_time": 64750.0,
      "text": "about how to move forward."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 64750.0,
      "end_time": 67440.0,
      "text": "So just who are the users of financial information"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 67440.0,
      "end_time": 71050.0,
      "text": "and what information do they need to make decisions?"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 71050.0,
      "end_time": 72850.0,
      "text": "Users of accounting information are"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 72850.0,
      "end_time": 75910.0,
      "text": "individuals who have questions about an organization."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 75910.0,
      "end_time": 78340.0,
      "text": "And they need information to find answers and make"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 78340.0,
      "end_time": 79870.0,
      "text": "smart decisions."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 79870.0,
      "end_time": 81700.0,
      "text": "They analyze what happened in the past"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 81700.0,
      "end_time": 84760.0,
      "text": "in order to predict what may happen in the future."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 84760.0,
      "end_time": 87280.0,
      "text": "To do that, they need detailed accounting information"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 87280.0,
      "end_time": 89140.0,
      "text": "on a timely basis."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 89140.0,
      "end_time": 90730.0,
      "text": "There are really two types of users"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 90730.0,
      "end_time": 95320.0,
      "text": "of accounting information, internal and external users."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 95320.0,
      "end_time": 99620.0,
      "text": "Internal users plan, organize, and run businesses."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 99620.0,
      "end_time": 101630.0,
      "text": "They ask questions such as, what price"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 101630.0,
      "end_time": 104510.0,
      "text": "should we charge for our product or service?"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 104510.0,
      "end_time": 107870.0,
      "text": "Should we expand on global markets or not?"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 107870.0,
      "end_time": 111830.0,
      "text": "What products are profitable and which should be discontinued?"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 111830.0,
      "end_time": 114980.0,
      "text": "Internal users have access to a large amount of information."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 114980.0,
      "end_time": 119160.0,
      "text": "And they will not be a focus of this course."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 119160.0,
      "end_time": 122190.0,
      "text": "External users are outside of an organization."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 122190.0,
      "end_time": 124170.0,
      "text": "They depend on financial statements"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 124170.0,
      "end_time": 127010.0,
      "text": "in order to make informed decisions."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 127010.0,
      "end_time": 129320.0,
      "text": "Investors, lenders, and other creditors"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 129320.0,
      "end_time": 132620.0,
      "text": "are the key external users of accounting information."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 132620.0,
      "end_time": 135500.0,
      "text": "They make resource allocation decisions."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 135500.0,
      "end_time": 137300.0,
      "text": "That means that their decisions generally"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 137300.0,
      "end_time": 139250.0,
      "text": "involve the giving up or receiving"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 139250.0,
      "end_time": 142620.0,
      "text": "of cash, goods, or services."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 142620.0,
      "end_time": 146030.0,
      "text": "So what questions do the main external users have?"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 146030.0,
      "end_time": 149840.0,
      "text": "Well, an investor might ask if a business is profitable enough"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 149840.0,
      "end_time": 152360.0,
      "text": "to give them a return on their investment."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 152360.0,
      "end_time": 154040.0,
      "text": "A lender might ask if a business will"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 154040.0,
      "end_time": 156350.0,
      "text": "be able to repay a loan plus interest,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 156350.0,
      "end_time": 158300.0,
      "text": "when the loan comes due."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 158300.0,
      "end_time": 160360.0,
      "text": "And other creditors might ask if the bills"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 160360.0,
      "end_time": 164450.0,
      "text": "a company has outstanding will be paid in the future."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 164450.0,
      "end_time": 168440.0,
      "text": "There are other external users that might also have questions."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 168440.0,
      "end_time": 170420.0,
      "text": "Employees and labor unions want to know"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 170420.0,
      "end_time": 174256.0,
      "text": "if they will receive higher wages or better benefits."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 174256.0,
      "end_time": 176630.0,
      "text": "Customers are interested in whether a business will honor"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 176630.0,
      "end_time": 179080.0,
      "text": "their warranties in the future."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 179080.0,
      "end_time": 181210.0,
      "text": "Tax agencies, like Revenue Canada,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 181210.0,
      "end_time": 185080.0,
      "text": "want to know if an organization is paying appropriate taxes."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 185080.0,
      "end_time": 188650.0,
      "text": "Regulatory agencies, like the Securities Exchange Commission,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 188650.0,
      "end_time": 190390.0,
      "text": "want to know if an organization is"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 190390.0,
      "end_time": 192910.0,
      "text": "in compliance with their rules."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 192910.0,
      "end_time": 194950.0,
      "text": "And finally, financial analysts want"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 194950.0,
      "end_time": 196960.0,
      "text": "to know if a company is one that they want"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 196960.0,
      "end_time": 199420.0,
      "text": "to recommend to their clients."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 199420.0,
      "end_time": 202450.0,
      "text": "But the key external users of accounting information"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 202450.0,
      "end_time": 206000.0,
      "text": "are still investors, lenders, and other creditors."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 206000.0,
      "end_time": 207640.0,
      "text": "This is because they are the users who"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 207640.0,
      "end_time": 210990.0,
      "text": "make decisions about resources."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 210990.0,
      "end_time": 212850.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s important to check your understanding."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 212850.0,
      "end_time": 215160.0,
      "text": "And the best way to do that is to test yourself."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 215160.0,
      "end_time": 217860.0,
      "text": "Periodically, you&#39;re going to see multiple choice questions."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 217860.0,
      "end_time": 219750.0,
      "text": "I recommend that you pause the video"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 219750.0,
      "end_time": 222150.0,
      "text": "and answer the questions yourself, before you check"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 222150.0,
      "end_time": 225110.0,
      "text": "to see if you got it right."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 225110.0,
      "end_time": 228170.0,
      "text": "Determining if a company can pay its obligations as they"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 228170.0,
      "end_time": 230872.0,
      "text": "come due is the primary objective of which"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 230872.0,
      "end_time": 231830.0,
      "text": "of the following users?"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 237050.0,
      "end_time": 239540.0,
      "text": "The primary objective of investors, competitors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 239540.0,
      "end_time": 242360.0,
      "text": "and labor unions is not whether a company can pay its bills"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 242360.0,
      "end_time": 243770.0,
      "text": "when they come due."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 243770.0,
      "end_time": 248240.0,
      "text": "Yes, those external users are concerned about that."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 248240.0,
      "end_time": 250520.0,
      "text": "But it&#39;s not their primary concern."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 250520.0,
      "end_time": 254060.0,
      "text": "Creditors, also called lenders, have a primary objective,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 254060.0,
      "end_time": 255710.0,
      "text": "and that is whether the company is"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 255710.0,
      "end_time": 259010.0,
      "text": "able to pay their bills as they come due."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 259010.0,
      "end_time": 262010.0,
      "text": "What about ethics and accounting information?"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 262010.0,
      "end_time": 264200.0,
      "text": "In order for accounting information to be useful,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 264200.0,
      "end_time": 266930.0,
      "text": "it must represent the actual economic activity"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 266930.0,
      "end_time": 271330.0,
      "text": "of an organization, what we call the underlying truth."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 271330.0,
      "end_time": 272930.0,
      "text": "Preparers of accounting information"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 272930.0,
      "end_time": 276260.0,
      "text": "have extensive rules of conduct to guide what they report,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 276260.0,
      "end_time": 278450.0,
      "text": "when they report it, and how they present it"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 278450.0,
      "end_time": 280490.0,
      "text": "to interested users."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 280490.0,
      "end_time": 282620.0,
      "text": "Without ethics in accounting, the information"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 282620.0,
      "end_time": 284990.0,
      "text": "produced by accounting information systems"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 284990.0,
      "end_time": 287300.0,
      "text": "would be useless for decision making."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 287300.0,
      "end_time": 290180.0,
      "text": "Following incorrect information would result in"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 290180.0,
      "end_time": 293720.0,
      "text": "not only possibly a financial crisis, but also"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 293720.0,
      "end_time": 296390.0,
      "text": "reduced confidence in the information provided"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 296390.0,
      "end_time": 298400.0,
      "text": "by accounting systems."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 298400.0,
      "end_time": 300650.0,
      "text": "Ethics in accounting is critical to the health"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 300650.0,
      "end_time": 303290.0,
      "text": "of a business and also financial markets."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 303290.0,
      "end_time": 304880.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s a key focus when preparing"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 304880.0,
      "end_time": 307390.0,
      "text": "accounting information."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 307390.0,
      "end_time": 309130.0,
      "text": "In the next video, we&#39;ll be talking"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 309130.0,
      "end_time": 312010.0,
      "text": "about the three main types of organizations"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 312010.0,
      "end_time": 315990.0,
      "text": "and the main activities that businesses engage in."
    }
  ]
}